{"tid":2343752,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消息：本港新增超過60宗確診 多2名患者離世","createTime":"2020-12-28T07:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T08:14:39.000Z","uid":293677,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9b3aaf44230cb4c0771ea7581da1459daadb73f6","tid":2343752,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:32:20.000Z","msg":"最後更新時間 28.12.2020 14:42<br />\n<br />\n消息指，本港新增超過60宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"> 再多2名新型冠狀病毒患者離世</span></span>。一名聯合醫院2D懷安科病房<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">有末期病患的74歲女病人</span></span>，她本月16日晚上因氣促入院，情況持續惡化，延至凌晨1時19分離世，成為聯合醫院群組爆發的首名死者；<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">另一名有長期病患的73歲男患者，與歌舞群組有關</span></span>，上月24日確診入住明愛醫院，情況持續惡化，延至今日凌晨離世。本港至今累計139名患者離世。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2372467&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=ea2695b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372467</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">老舞群組做到野</span></span>"},{"pid":"96d2c0170d16e49c5e21f75a7a22264a2a753915","tid":2343752,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cdde6569f98029e94a028c369d0d0bd5f071f6b","tid":2343752,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yhEkIPHdoW8CbfuIA2k5EEnKmko=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RUP5P6ZDZZHB5MRIRCJKCIUNTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyhEkIPHdoW8CbfuIA2k5EEnKmko%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fap